C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENaomi%20Ackie%20as%20Frida%20and%20Channing%20Tatum%20as%20Slater%20King%20in%20%26quot%3BBlink%20Twice.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECarlos%20Somonte%2FAmazon%20MGM%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EZo%C3%AB%20Kravitz's%20psychological%20thriller%20%26quot%3BBlink%20Twice%26quot%3B%20stars%20Naomi%20Ackie%20and%20Channing%20Tatum.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20film%20takes%20place%20on%20a%20private%20island%20where%20strange%20things%20happen.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20what%20to%20know%20about%20the%20movie's%20action-filled%20ending.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWarning%3A%20Major%20spoilers%20ahead%20for%20%26quot%3BBlink%20Twice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBlink%20Twice%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20new%20psychological%20thriller%20cowritten%20and%20directed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchanning-tatum-zoe-kravitz-relationship-timeline-photos-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZo%C3%AB%20Kravitz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20stuffed%20with%20twists%20and%20turns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKravitz's%20directorial%20debut%20stars%20Naomi%20Ackie%20as%20Frida%2C%20a%20cocktail%20waitress%20and%20aspiring%20nail%20artist%20in%20desperate%20need%20of%20a%20vacation.%20She%20meets%20tech%20billionaire%20Slater%20King%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchanning-tatum-deadpool-and-wolverine-gambit-movie-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChanning%20Tatum%3C%2Fa%3E)%20while%20working%20at%20a%20lavish%20gala%20for%20his%20company%2C%20King-Tech.%20Frida%20charms%20her%20way%20into%20a%20trip%20to%20his%20private%20island%20with%20her%20best%20friend%20Jess%20(Alia%20Shawkat).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhones%20are%20swiftly%20surrendered%2C%20and%20Frida%20loses%20track%20of%20the%20days%20as%20she%20falls%20into%20a%20cycle%20of%20drinking%2C%20smoking%2C%20doing%20drugs%2C%20and%20partying%20with%20Slater%20and%20his%20posse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20take%20too%20long%20before%20Frida%20starts%20noticing%20unsettling%20peculiarities%2C%20like%20unexplained%20dirt%20under%20her%20fingernails%20and%20a%20maid%20killing%20the%20island's%20venomous%20snakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20Frida%20pieces%20together%20the%20sinister%20things%20really%20happening%20on%20the%20island%2C%20the%20action%20kicks%20into%20high%20gear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20breakdown%20of%20the%20film's%20climax%20and%20satisfying%20ending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22942f2d63-2657-4eb3-94a9-b46f87d39aa4%5C%22%3EFrida%20and%20Sarah%20team%20up%20to%20take%20down%20Slater%20and%20the%20men%20who%20have%20been%20abusing%20and%20exploiting%20the%20women.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Naomi%20Ackie%20as%20Frida%20and%20Adria%20Arjona%20as%20Sarah%20in%20%26quot%3BBlink%20Twice.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c5fa5b1aa2ac29ee32d786%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22791%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENaomi%20Ackie%20as%20Frida%20and%20Adria%20Arjona%20as%20Sarah%20in%20%26quot%3BBlink%20Twice.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EAmazon%20MGM%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESlater%20is%20initially%20presented%20as%20a%20charming%20billionaire%20who%20credits%20therapy%20with%20changing%20his%20life.%20But%20his%20sadistic%20behavior%20becomes%20clearer%20later%20in%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Jess%20gets%20bitten%20by%20a%20viper%20one%20night%2C%20she%20decides%20she's%20had%20enough%20of%20the%20island.%20But%20Frida%20has%20no%20desire%20to%20leave%20because%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20her%20life%2C%20she's%20not%20invisible.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20Frida%20wakes%20up%20and%20goes%20about%20her%20typical%20routine%3A%20spraying%20herself%20with%20a%20perfume%20made%20from%20a%20red%20desideria%20flower%20found%20only%20on%20the%20island%2C%20getting%20dressed%20in%20the%20same%20white%20outfit%2C%20and%20joining%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20group%20for%20another%20day%20of%20relaxation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20maid%20gives%20Frida%20a%20green%20liquid%20to%20drink%20that's%20actually%20snake%20venom%2C%20she%20begins%20to%20regain%20fragments%20of%20memories.%20Another%20guest%20on%20the%20island%20named%20Sarah%20(Adria%20Arjona)%20then%20confides%20in%20Frida%20and%20says%20she's%20having%20a%20good%20time%20but%20also%20has%20a%20weird%20feeling%20that%20something's%20off%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20considering%20that%20none%20of%20the%20women%20besides%20Frida%20have%20any%20memory%20of%20Jess%2C%20who%20vanished%20without%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrida%20and%20Sarah%20figure%20out%20that%20the%20perfume%20is%20erasing%20the%20women's%20memories%20and%20that%20snake%20venom%20is%20the%20key%20to%20remembering.%20To%20help%20the%20other%20women%20regain%20their%20memories%20without%20raising%20suspicion%2C%20Frida%20and%20Sarah%20give%20them%20tequila%20shots%20mixed%20with%20venom.%20Stacey%20(Geena%20Davis)%2C%20Slater's%20scatter-brained%20assistant%2C%20also%20takes%20venom-laced%20shots%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Naomi%20Ackie%20as%20Frida%20and%20Adria%20Arjona%20as%20Sarah%20in%20%26quot%3BBlink%20Twice.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c6408d5da406397bf7c46f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAckie%20as%20Frida%20and%20Arjona%20as%20Sarah%20in%20%26quot%3BBlink%20Twice.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECarlos%20Somonte%2FAmazon%20MGM%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrida%20regains%20more%20of%20her%20memories%20and%20learns%20that%20Jess%20was%20murdered%20by%20the%20men%20because%20the%20snake%20bite%20prevented%20her%20from%20forgetting.%20Moreover%2C%20Frida%20and%20the%20other%20women%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20varying%20degrees%20of%20sexual%20violence%20by%20Slater%20and%20the%20other%20men%