e%20in%20luxury%20buildings%2C%20with%20amenities%20like%20conference%20rooms%2C%20gyms%2C%20recreational%20areas%2C%20and%20even%20one%20that%20had%20a%20swimming%20pool%20%E2%80%94%20things%20that%20I%20could%20only%20fantasize%20about%20while%20living%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apartments.com%2Frent-market-trends%2Fportland-me%2F%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApartments.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20average%20cost%20of%20renting%20a%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20Portland%20in%20August%202024%20is%20around%20%241%2C695%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20is%20still%2010%25%20higher%20than%20the%20national%20average%20of%20%241%2C536%20a%20month%2C%20New%20York%20City%20one-bedrooms%20run%20for%20a%20staggering%20%243%2C801%20a%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apartments.com%2Frent-market-trends%2Fnew-york-ny%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20site%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20apartments%20I%20toured%20were%20all%20higher%20than%20the%20average%20cost%20in%20Portland%20but%20still%20lower%20than%20the%20average%20cost%20of%20one-bedroom%20apartments%20in%20New%20York%2C%20which%20made%20me%20question%20whether%20Portland%20could%20be%20a%20better%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20all%20three%20apartments%20compared%20in%20terms%20of%20price%2C%20location%2C%20and%20amenities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20first%20apartment%20building%20I%20viewed%20was%20The%20Armature%20in%20Portland's%20Bayside%20neighborhood.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Armature%20apartment%20complex%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7627243b5e59d16b4583f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Armature%20apartment%20building%20was%20modern%20on%20the%20outside%20with%20wooden%20accents.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%