.%20These%20networks%20also%20help%20Russian%20oligarchs%20circumvent%20prior%20restrictions%2C%20the%20Treasury%20said%2C%20and%20have%20helped%20one%20company%20launder%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20Russia%2C%20IT%20and%20software%20companies%20essential%20to%20the%20country's%20financial%20sector%20were%20also%20targeted%2C%20and%20curbs%20on%20metal%20and%20mining%20revenue%20were%20extended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20dragging%20on%20through%20its%20third%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-sanctions-circumvent-buying-2nd-hand-tech-defense-industry-moscow-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%20has%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Russia's%20defense%20ministry%20continues%20to%20access%20needed%20equipment%20through%20secondhand%20markets%2C%20relying%20on%20opaque%20firms%20to%20source%20essential%20products.%20Foreign%20markets%20have%20increasingly%20served%20as%20a%20lifeline%20for%20the%20Kremlin%2C%20and%20the%20West%20has%20not%20ceased%20in%20its%20attempt%20to%20end%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202023%2C%20an%20executive%20order%20gave%20the%20US%20Treasury%20new%20power%20to%20unleash%20secondary%20sanctions%20on%20financial%20institutions%20that%20work%20with%20Russia.%20This%20has%20shown%20results%2C%20such%20as%20in%20China%20%E2%80%94%20a%20recent%20report%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-all-china-banks-refuse-yuan-ruble-transfers-sanctions-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%20all%20Chinese%20banks%20are%20now%20refusing%20payments%20from%20Russia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20impeding%20the%20Kremlin's%20ability%20to%20bypass%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20trade%20data%20cited%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F7d6a40c5-fa19-4cd0-a214-d6deef53bae7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20war-linked%20exports%20from%20Ch