at%20someone%20big%20might%20make%20a%20surprise%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20betting%20markets%20like%20Polymarket%20thought%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20was%20an%20odds-on%20favorite%20to%20perform.%20People%20at%20the%20DNC%20were%20telling%20other%20people%20at%20the%20DNC%20that%20they%20had%20heard%20that%20%3Cem%3Eother%3C%2Fem%3E%20people%20were%20sure%20she%20was%20going%20to%20make%20a%20blockbuster%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20main%20reason%20many%20reasonable%20people%20assumed%20this%20was%20a%20done%20deal%20was%20that%20TMZ%20said%20it%20was%20going%20to%20happen%3A%20%26quot%3BExclusive%3A%20BEYONC%C3%89%20PERFORMING%20AT%20DNC'S%20FINAL%20NIGHT!!!%26quot%3B%20the%20site%20proclaimed%20at%207%3A49%20p.m.%20ET%2C%20just%20before%20most%20networks%20started%20their%20prime-time%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20site's%20story%20was%20cited%20throughout%20the%20media%20ecosystem%2C%20including%20normally%20staid%2C%20by-the-book%20outlets%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fsinger-beyonce-perform-dnc-thursday-tmz-reports-2024-08-23%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Flivecoverage%2Fdnc-harris-speech-election-2024%2Fcard%2Ftmz-reports-beyonc-will-perform-2ipVi0rGrSkj2WRq9DpB%3Fmod%3Dmhp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20TMZ's%20story%20didn't%20change%20throughout%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20DNC's%20last%20night%20%E2%80%94%20even%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-news%2Fbeyonce-not-attending-2024-dnc-1235982694%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeyonc%C3%A9's%20rep%20had%20told%20The%20Hollywood%20Reporter%20she%20was%20not%20performing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20even%20after%20Harris%20had%20finished%20her%20acceptance%20speech%20and%20balloons%20were%20filling%20the%20stage%20at%20the%20United%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%20%E2%80%94%20at%2012%3A30%20a.m.%20ET%20on%20Friday%2C%20TMZ%20fessed%20up%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tmz.com%2F2024%2F08%2F22%2Fbeyonce-dnc-final-night-kamala-harris%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBEYONC%C3%89%20NOT%20AT%20DNC%20AFTER%20ALL%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20acknowledged.%20%26quot%3BTo%20quote%20the%20great%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tmz.com%2Fpeople%2Fbeyonce-knowles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeyonc%C3%A9%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20We%20gotta%20lay%20our%20cards%20down%2C%20down%2C%20down%20...%20we%20got%20this%20one%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20me%2C%20the%20interesting%20part%20of%20the%20story%20isn't%20that%20TMZ%20blew%20it%2C%20or%20even%20how%20it%20blew%20it%20%E2%80%94%20though%20I'd%20certainly%20love%20to%20hear%20the%20backstory.%20(I've%20asked%20TMZ%20for%20comment.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20that%20in%202024%2C%20for%20much%20of%20the%20modern%20media%20world%2C%20a%20TMZ%20report%20is%20pretty%20close%20to%20accepted%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%2C%20TMZ%20was%20considered%20less%20than%20by%20conventional%20media%20%E2%80%94%20a%20gossip%20operation%20that%20was%20pretty%20close%20to%20the%20National%20Enquirer.%20Sometimes%20wrong%2C%20sometimes%20right%2C%20always%20salacious.%20But%20never%20something%20you'd%20admit%20to%20consuming%20in%20polite%20company%2C%20let%20alone%20reprinting%20in%20a%20Serious%20News%20Operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETMZ%20%E2%80%94%20both%20the%20site%20and%20the%20associated%20TV%20show%20%E2%80%94%20are%20now%20owned%20by%20Rupert%20Murdoch's%20News%20Corp.%20It%20started%20out%20as%20part%20of%20the%20company%20formerly%20known%20as%20Time%20Warner%2C%20and%20launched%20in%202005%2C%20when%20the%20internet%20was%20still%20a%20curiosity%20to%20lots%20of%20media%20grown-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20years%2C%20the%20site%20and%20Harvey%20Levin%20%E2%80%94%20its%20operator%20and%20figurehead%20%E2%80%94%20fascinated%20big%20media%2C%20too%3A%20They%20wrote%20profiles%20about%20him%20and%20his%20operation's%20bare-knuckled%20approach%20to%20gathering%20celebrity%20news.%20TMZ%20paid%20tipsters%20for%20information%20%E2%80%94%20a%20no-no%20in%20American%20media%20%E2%80%94%20and%20often%20published%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20could%2C%20even%20when%20the%20subjects%20it%20was%20reporting%20on%20claimed%20the%20news%20was%20false.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20me%2C%20TMZ's%20big%20breakthrough%20as%20a%20Real%20News%20Source%20was%20when%20it%20broke%20the%20news%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tmz.com%2F2009%2F06%2F25%2Fmichael-jackson-dies-death-dead-cardiac-arrest%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMichael%20Jackson's%20death%20in%202009%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20was%20a%20seismic%2C%20worldwide%20event%2C%20and%20it%20came%20just%20as%20the%20world%20was%20starting%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20news%20could%20jump%20from%20a%20left-field%20site%20to%20digital%20distributors%20like%20Facebook%20and%20Twitter%2C%20without%20the%20mediation%20of%20traditional%20news%20publishers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20underscored%20one%20of%20TMZ's%20real%20strengths%20%E2%80%94%20getting%20people%20around%20famous%20people%20(sometimes%20their%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20sometimes%20people%20in%20coroners'%20offices%20or%20other%20institutions)%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fnews%2Flocal-news%2Ftmz-hollywood-obituaries-1235648344%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshare%20the%20news%20about%20famous%20people%20dying%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202016%2C%20when%20TMZ%20broke%20the%20news%20of%20Prince's%20death%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Flifestyle%2Fstyle%2Ftmz-was-first--again-will-their-word-alone-ever-be-good-enough-for-traditional-media%2F2016%2F04%2F22%2F822613ae-0805-11e6-bdcb-0133da18418d_story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%20pointed%20out%20that%20TMZ%20did%20this%20sort%20of%20thing%20all%20the%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20yet%20traditional%20outlets%20were%20loath%20to%20cite%20it%2C%20and%20often%20waited%20for%20other%20sources%20instead%20%E2%80%94%20even%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20consumed%20the%20TMZ%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20delayed%20reaction%20illustrates%20a%20paradox%20about%20TMZ%3A%20Although%20it%20has%20been%20quite%20reliable%20on%20many%20major%20stories%2C%20mainstream%20news%20sources%20are%20reluctant%20to%20rely%20on%20its%20say-so%20alone.%20The%20news%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20doesn't%20become%20news%20until%20another%20source%20matches%20TMZ's%20reporting.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3ETMZ's%20go-go-go%20approach%20still%20gets%20stuff%20wrong.%20And%20Levin's%20chumminess%20with%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20led%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.thinkprogress.org%2Ftmz-quietly-became-americas-most-potent-pro-trump-media-outlet-bf703c24a68e%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20site's%20no-holds-barred%20approach%20to%20news%20may%20actually%20have%20some%20bars%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Trump%20(again%2C%20drawing%20a%20parallel%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F04%2F24%2Fmedia%2Fnational-enquirer-trump-protect-smear%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20National%20Enquirer%2C%20which%20literally%20worked%20on%20Trump's%20behalf%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20for%20lots%20of%20people%20%E2%80%94%20even%20people%20who%20run%20Serious%20News%20Organizations%20%E2%80%94%20TMZ%20is%20now%20fully%20considered%20a%20legitimate%20news%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you%20still%20aren't%20convinced%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fabbydphillip%2Fstatus%2F1826825120909771181%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DxhuXMba3HM4poWm9CQq-PA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esee%20this%20tweet%20from%20CNN's%20Abby%20Phillip%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20declared%20that%20%26quot%3BTMZ%20lost%20a%20lot%20of%20credibility%20tonight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can't%20lose%20it%20unless%20you%20already%20have%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeyonce-dnc-tmz-media-gossip-kamala-harris-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724436892000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8d06b43b5e59d16b4c66f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeyonce-dnc-tmz-media-gossip-kamala-harris-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TMZ%20used%20to%20be%20a%20gossip%20site%20the%20Media%20World%20tried%20to%20ignore.%20Now%20media%20organizations%20take%20it%20seriously%20%E2%80%94%20even%20when%20it%20gets%20the%20story%20wrong.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pkafka%40insider.com%20(Peter%20Kafka)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A73%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeyonce-dnc-tmz-media-gossip-kamala-harris-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kailsh%20Kher%20on%2020%20years%20of%20close%20bond%20with%20AR%20Rahman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724436797000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112747561%2Cimgsize-24092.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkailsh-kher-reflects-on-20-years-of-close-bond-with-ar-rahman-i-was-very-close-to-his-mother-and-sister%2Farticleshow%2F112747561.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112747561.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKailash%20Kher%20and%20AR%20Rahman%E2%80%99s%20collaboration%20is%20more%20than%20just%20musical%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20deep%2C%20familial%20b