the%20press%20and%20social%20media%20as%20belonging%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BKuki-Zo%26quot%3B%20tribes.%20The%20three%20MLAs%2C%20however%2C%20in%20statements%20in%20the%20last%20two%20days%20said%20the%20term%20%26quot%3BKuki-Zo%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20adequate%20to%20refer%20to%20their%20own%20tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20MLAs%20from%20the%20Hmar%2C%20Paite%2C%20and%20Vaiphei%20tribes%20who%20issued%20the%20statements%20are%20LM%20Khaute%2C%20Ngursanglur%20Sanate%2C%20and%20Vungzagin%20Valte.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20I%20would%20like%20to%20reaffirm%20that%20the%20most%20suitable%20and%20inclusive%20term%20to%20describe%20our%20community%20in%20the%20media%2C%20social%20media%20and%20so%20on%20is%20'Kuki-Zomi-Hmar...%20I%20cannot%20accept%20anything%20that%20excludes%20'Zomi'%20and%20any%20other%20term%20that%20describes%20our%20identity%20in%20such%20press%20statements%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khaute%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sanate%20said%20he%20will%20not%20endorse%20any%20platform%2C%20organisation%20or%20statement%20that%20excludes%20the%20term%20%26quot%3BHmar%26quot%3B%20tribe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20MLA%2C%20Mr%20Valte%2C%20in%20a%20strongly%20worded%20statement%20said%20it%20has%20become%20%26quot%3Bpivotal%26quot%3B%20for%20him%20to%20declare%20that%20he%20is%20from%20the%20Paite%20tribe%20belonging%20to%20the%20Zomi%20community%2C%20that%20Zomi%20is%20an%20accepted%20nomenclature%20as%20it%20reflects%20the%20%26quot%3Btrue%20historical%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20social%20identity%20of%20our%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20The%20recent%20usage%20of%20'Kuki-Zo'%20is%20perceived%20by%20many%20within%20my%20represented%20communities%20as%20non-inclusive%20and%20assimilative...%20Therefore%2C%20I%20cannot%2C%20in%20good%20conscience%2C%20accept%20and%20endorse%20any%20term%20that%20doesn't%20respect%20the%20individuality%20and%20dignity%20of%20all%20the%20groups%20that%20form%20the%20fabric%20of%20my%20constituency%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Valte.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20MLAs'%20statements%20come%20days%20after%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Thadou%20tribes%20represented%20by%20the%20Manipur-based%20Thadou%20Students'%20Association%20(TSA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-are-not-kuki-says-manipurs-thadou-tribe-waits-for-peace-plan-from-chief-minister-n-biren-singh-6346137%5C%22%3Eformed%20a%20global%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20look%20into%20critical%20issues%20facing%20the%20community%2C%20particularly%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TSA%20has%20said%20Thadou%20is%20a%20distinct%20tribe%20and%20people%20with%20their%20own%20distinct%20identity%2C%20language%20and%20culture.%20%26quot%3B...%20At%20some%20point%20other%20people%20may%20have%20called%20Thadous%20with%20different%20names...%20that%20does%20not%20change%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20are%20Thadou%20and%20we%20should%20be%20called%20Thadou%20respectfully%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20TSA%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20August%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20BJP%20spokesperson%20T%20Michael%20Lamjathang%20Haokip%2C%20who%20is%20from%20the%20Thadou%20tribe%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20said%20the%20three%20Hmar%2C%20Paite%2C%20and%20Vaiphei%20MLAs'%20statements%20%26quot%3Bhave%20explicitly%20stated%20they%20are%20not%20Kuki%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20the%20true%20identity%20of%20Kuki.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20The%20remaining%207%20MLAs%20should%20adhere%20to%20their%20tribe%20identities%20to%20reach%20a%20common%20consensus.%20The%20individual%20statements%20of%20the%203%20MLAs%20signify%20their%20rejection%20of%20Kuki%20supremacists...%20The%20disunited%20Zo%20tribal%20groups%2C%20united%20only%20in%20their%20desire%20to%20remove%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20hostility%20against%20the%20Meitei%2C%20must%20cease%20targeting%20innocent%20lives%20and%20work%20towards%20a%20peaceful%20solution.%20The%20proxy%20unity%20aimed%20at%20ousting%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20political%20gains%20should%20not%20come%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20innocent%20lives%20and%20communal%20harmony%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Michael%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FTMLH4BJP%2Fstatus%2F1826923750899462428%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fg04lcikg_michael_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20discussion%20and%20voting%20on%20demands%20for%20grants%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20session%20on%20August%2012%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20had%20said%20%26quot%3Bviolence%20was%20perpetrated%20by%20some%2C%20not%20all%2C%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20every%20Thadou%2C%20Paite%2C%20Hmar%20had%20a%20hand%20in%20the%20violence.%20You%20have%20seen%2C%20Hmar%20people%20spoke%20so%20well%20(in%20the%20peace%20meeting)%2C%20we%20had%20tears%2C%20they%20too%20had%20tears%2C%20that%20all%20this%20happened%20due%20to%20misunderstandings%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20had%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20August%201%20peace%20meeting%20between%20Meitei%20and%20the%20Hmar%20tribe%20representatives%20in%20Jiribam%2C%20where%20they%20agreed%20to%20work%20for%20normalcy%20nearly%20two%20months%20after%20ethnic%20violence%20that%20began%20over%20a%20year%20ago%20reached%20the%20district%20bordering%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clashes%20between%20the%20valley-dominant%20Meitei%20community%20and%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20tribes%20known%20as%20Kukis%20-%20a%20term%20given%20by%20the%20British%20in%20colonial%20times%20-%20who%20are%20dominant%20in%20some%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%2C%20has%20killed%20over%20220%20people%20and%20internally%20displaced%20nearly%2050%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20category%20Meiteis%20want%20to%20be%20included%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20category%2C%20while%20the%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20tribes%20that%20share%20ethnic%20ties%20with%20people%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar's%20Chin%20State%20and%20Mizoram%20want%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur%2C%20citing%20discrimination%20and%20unequal%20share%20of%20resources%20and%20power%20with%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724432280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fg9kvcgho_kuki-mla_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkuki-zo-wrong-term-to-describe-us-say-3-manipur-mlas-from-different-tribes-6403567%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20MLAs%20from%20among%20the%2010%20who%20have%20been%20demanding%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur%20have%20clarified%20that%20they%20want%20their%20own%20tribes%20to%20be%20called%20by%20their%20correct%20names%2C%20instead%20of%20being%20associated%20only%20with%20the%20term%20%26quot%3BKuki-Zo%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkuki-zo-wrong-term-to-describe-us-say-3-manipur-mlas-from-different-tribes-6403567%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHistory%20Made%20Today%2C%26quot%3B%20Says%20Zelensky%20After%20Meeting%20PM%20Modi%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BFollowing%20the%20visit%2C%20we%20also%20agreed%20on%20a%20joint%20statement%20focusing%20on%20the%20development%20of%20a%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20bilateral%20trade%2C%20and%20continued%20military-technical%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Ukrainian%20President%2C%20whose%20country%20is%20at%20war%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi's%20office%20in%20the%20joint%20India-Ukraine%20statement%20said%20both%20leaders%20reiterated%20their%20readiness%20for%20further%20cooperation%20in%20upholding%20principles%20of%20international%20law%2C%20including%20the%20UN%20Charter%2C%20such%20as%20respect%20for%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20sovereignty%20of%20states.%20%26quot%3BThey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-ukraine-visit-pm-modi-holds-talks-with-ukraine-president-in-kyiv-full-joint-statement-6402100%5C%22%3Eagreed%20on%20the%20desirability%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20closer%20bilateral%20dialogue%20in%20this%20regard%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20joint%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi%20arrived%20in%20Kyiv%20this%20morning%20on%20a%20special%20train%20on%20the%20first-ever%20visit%20to%20Ukraine%20by%20an%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20after%20the%20former%20Russian%20state%20became%20independent%20in%201991.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20his%20talks%20with%20Mr%20Zelenskyy%20that%20took%20place%20under%20the%20shadow%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20India%20is%20ever%20ready%20to%20play%20an%20%26quot%3Bactive%20role%26quot%3B%20in%20every%20effort%20to%20restore%20peace%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20he%20would%20even%20like%20to%20contribute%20personally%20in%20ending%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20(India)%20are%20not%20neutral.%20From%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20we%20have%20taken%20sides.%20And%20we%20have%20chosen%20the%20side%20of%20peace.%20We%20have%20come%20from%20the%20land%20of%20Buddha%20where%20there%20is%20no%20place%20for%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20his%20opening%20remarks%20during%20the%20talks.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20come%20from%20the%20land%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20who%20had%20given%20a%20message%20of%20peace%20to%20the%20entire%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBoth%20sides%20agreed%20to%20ask%20the%20Indian-Ukrainian%20Intergovernmental%20Commission%20(IGC)%20to%20explore%20all%20possible%20ways%20to%20not%20only%20restore%20bilateral%20trade%20and%20economic%20relations%20to%20pre-conflict%20levels%2C%20but%20expand%20and%20deepen%20them%20further.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20reduction%20in%20the%20annual%20bilateral%20trade%20in%20goods%20since%202022%20due%20to%20the%20challenges%20related%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20apprised%20Mr%20Zelensky%20of%20his%20conversations%20with%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20in%20Samarkand%20in%20September%202022%20and%20Moscow%20last%20month.%20%26quot%3BSome%20time%20back%2C%20when%20I%20met%20President%20Putin%20in%20Samarkand%2C%20I%20had%20told%20him%20that%20this%20was%20not%20the%20era%20of%20war.%20Last%20month%20when%20I%20went%20to%20Russia%2C%20I%20said%20in%20clear%20words%20that%20a%20solution%20to%20any%20problem%20is%20never%20found%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Kyiv%20is%20seen%20in%20many%20quarters%20as%20a%20diplomatic%20balancing%20act%20as%20his%20trip%20to%20Russia%20triggered%20anguish%20among%20some%20Western%20countries.%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20PM%20Modi%20reiterated%20the%20need%20for%20%26quot%3Bpractical%20engagement%26quot%3B%20between%20all%20stakeholders%20to%20develop%20an%20innovative%20solution%20that%20will%20help%20build%20broad%20acceptability%20and%20contribute%20towards%20peace%20and%20stability.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBoth%20sides%20called%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20reform%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20to%20reflect%20contemporary%20global%20realities%20and%20to%20make%20it%20more%20representative%2C%20effective%20and%20efficient%20in%20dealing%20with%20issues%20of%20international%20peace%20and%20security.%20Ukraine%20reiterated%20its%20support%20for%20India's%20permanent%20membership%20of%20a%20reformed%20and%20expanded%20UN%20Security%20Council.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724432160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fj46tltsg_pm-modi-and-zelensky_625x300_23_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhistory-made-today-says-ukraine-president-volodymyr-zelensky-after-meeting-pm-narendra-modi-10-points-6403784%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine's%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20today%20said%20history%20was%20made%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20first%20visit%20to%20Ukraine%20since%20the%20European%20country's%20independence.%20He%20said%20India%20and%20Ukraine%20have%20signed%20four%20documents%20on%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20fields.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20Export%20Strategy%20Causes%20Global%20Market%20Havoc%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChina's%20'Made%20in%20China'%20products%20have%20already%20established%20a%20firm%20foothold%20in%20the%20international%20market%2C%20surpassing%20the%20expansion%20of%20any%20other%20nation%20in%20history.%20Manufacturers%20all%20over%20the%20world%20are%20under%20tremendous%20pressure%20due%20to%20the%20flood%20of%20cheaper%20Chinese%20goods.%20China%20is%20now%20focussing%20more%20on%20exporting%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20take%20the%20lead%20in%20the%20world's%20manufacturing%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-trade-war-xi-manufacturing-49f81f68%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20has%20increased%20his%20focus%20on%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%2C%20with%20a%20high%20percentage%20of%20production%20going%20to%20export%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20slow%20economic%20development%20that%20his%20government%20is%20facing%20in%20recent%20past.%20China%20is%20once%20again%20ramping%20up%20its%20massive%20export%20machinery%2C%20giving%20rivals%20little%20opportunity%20to%20survive%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20China's%20manufacturing%20dominance%20is%20evident%20in%20various%20sectors.%20For%20instance%2C%20a%20Massachusetts%20startup%20called%20CubicPV%20betting%20on%20silicon%20wafers%2C%20a%20high-tech%20component%20in%20solar%20panels.%20Buoyed%20by%20President%20Biden's%20climate%20legislation%20enacted%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20with%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20tax%20credits%20and%20government%20loans%2C%20CubicPV%20announced%20plans%20in%20late%202022%20for%20a%20%241.4%20billion%20wafer%20plant%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20China%20has%20nearly%20doubled%20its%20output%20of%20silicon%20wafers-way%20more%20than%20it%20needs.%20The%20extra%20wafers%20had%20to%20go%20somewhere%2C%20and%20they%20went%20overseas%2C%20pushing%20prices%20down%20by%2070%25.%20CubicPV%20had%20to%20halt%20its%20production%20plan%20early%20this%20year%2C%20putting%20engineers%20and%20other%20employees%20out%20of%20work%2C%20citing%20%26quot%3Ba%20distorted%20market%20as%20a%20result%20of%20China's%20overcapacity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20case%2C%20thousands%20of%20miles%20away%2C%20in%20Chile%2C%20iron%20ore%20miner%20and%20steelmaker%20CAP%20is%20struggling%20with%20China's%20continued%20commitment%20to%20low-end%20commodity%20manufacturing%20as%20an%20onslaught%20of%20cheap%20Chinese%20metal%20hits%20its%20shores.%20The%20firm%20said%20this%20month%20that%20it%20would%20shutter%20its%20giant%20Huachipato%20steel%20mill%20in%20central%20Chile%20indefinitely%2C%20with%20the%20loss%20of%20some%202%2C200%20jobs.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20can't%20compete%20with%20low-priced%20Chinese%20metal%20even%20after%20the%20government%20raised%20tariffs%20on%20steel%20bars%20and%20other%20imported%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing's%20strategy%20of%20bolstering%20its%20manufacturing%20sector%20through%20aggressive%20exports%20is%20creating%20significant%20challenges%20for%20businesses%20around%20the%20world.%20This%20escalating%20trade%20tension%20raises%20concerns%20about%20the%20potential%20for%20a%20new%20global%20trade%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-trade-war-xi-manufacturing-49f81f68%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20WSJ%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20further%20mentioned%20that%20other%20countries%20have%20opened%20antidumping%20investigations%20to%20see%20whether%20Chinese%20goods%20are%20being%20sold%20below%20fair%20value.%20India%20is%20examining%20Chinese%20pigments%20and%20chemicals.%20Japan%20is%20looking%20at%20electrodes.%20The%20UK%20is%20investigating%20imports%20of%20excavators%20and%20biodiesel%2C%20while%20Argentina%20and%20Vietnam%20are%20probing%20Chinese%20microwave%20ovens%20and%20wind%20towers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXi%20Jinping's%20%26quot%3Bestablish%20the%20new%20before%20breaking%20the%20old%26quot%3B%20strategy%20prioritizes%20building%20new%20industries%20like%20EVs%20and%20semiconductors%20while%20maintaining%20traditional%20ones%20like%20steel.%20Despite%20acknowledging%20overcapacity%2C%20China%20continues%20to%20invest%20heavily%20in%20manufacturing%2C%20driven%20by%20concerns%20about%20industrial%20security%20and%20economic%20stability.%20This%20approach%20is%20straining%20global%20trade%20relations%20and%20causing%20economic%20hardship%20in%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724431980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F4afg8f8_chinas-aggressive-manufacturing_625x300_23_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-export-strategy-causes-global-market-havoc-report-6403729%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chinas%20aggressive%20manufacturing%20and%20export%20strategy%20under%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20driven%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Bestablish%20the%20new%20before%20breaking%20the%20old%26quot%3B%20policy%2C%20is%20intensifying%20global%20