uot%3BI%20am%20proud%20of%20my%20daughter%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gopala%2C%20who%20remembered%20Kamala%20Harris%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bnice%2C%20thoughtful%20child%26quot%3B%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20heartwarming%20stories%20of%20Ms%20Harris'%20childhood%2C%20her%20visits%20to%20India%20and%20their%20families'%20close%20bond%2C%20her%20aunt%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BKamala%20always%20calls%20me%20and%20my%20younger%20sister%20chitthi.%20She%20mentioned%20us%20and%20our%20brother%20in%20her%20Vice%20Presidential%20acceptance%20speech.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20mentioned%20an%20instance%20when%20Kamala%20Harris%20was%20visiting%20Chandigarh%3A%20%26quot%3BShe%20came%20to%20Chandigarh%20to%20visit%20me%20and%20she%20had%20a%20watch%20in%20her%20hand.%20I%20said%2C%20'Kamala%2C%20that's%20a%20nice%20watch'.%20And%20the%20next%20thing%20that%20happened%20was%20that%20she%20took%20out%20the%20watch%20and%20gave%20it%20to%20me.%20It%20had%20a%20gold%20strap%20and%20everything.%20She%20said%2C%20'You%20like%20it%2C%20you%20keep%20it%2C%20chitthi'.%20That's%20the%20kind%20of%20person%20she%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sarala%20Gopalan%2C%20Kamala%20Harriss%20aunt.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sarala%20Gopalan%2C%20Kamala%20Harriss%20aunt.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Ffbnouk0o_kamala-harris-chitthi_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sarala%20Gopalan%2C%20Kamala%20Harris's%20aunt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20speech%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%20remembered%20her%20trailblazer%20mother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-presidential-elections-kamala-harris-in-her-biggest-speech-yet-remembers-mother-dr-shyamala-gopalan-harris-6398395%5C%22%3EShyamala%20Gopalan%3C%2Fa%3E%20whom%20she%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20brilliant%205-foot%20tall%20brown%20woman%20with%20an%20accent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShyamala%20Gopalan%20was%20only%2019%20when%20she%20travelled%20from%20India%20to%20California%20with%20a%20dream%20to%20be%20the%20scientist%20who%20would%20cure%20breast%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20taught%20us%20to%20never%20complain%20about%20injustice%2C%20but%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it!%20Do%20something%20about%20it.%20That%20was%20our%20mother%2C%26quot%3B%20Kamala%20Harris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarala%20Gopalan%20recalled%20her%20sister%20Shyamala%20earned%20a%20US%20Fulbright%20scholarship%20on%20her%20own%20and%20her%20father%2C%20PV%20Gopalan%2C%20then%20an%20Indian%20bureaucrat%2C%20allowed%20her%20to%20study%20in%20the%20US.%20%26quot%3BOur%20father%20was%20particular%20about%20good%20education%20and%20he%20let%20her%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20sister%20Shyamala%20always%20stood%20up%20and%20fought%20for%20what%20was%20right.%20She%20taught%20her%20children%20to%20do%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Gopalan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Kamala%20Harris%20(R)%20with%20her%20mother%20(L)%20and%20chitthi%20(C).%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Kamala%20Harris%20(R)%20with%20her%20mother%20(L)%20and%20chitthi%20(C).%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fq7rns9v_kamala-chittis_625x300_23_August_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris%20(R)%20with%20her%20mother%20(L)%20and%20'chitthi'%20(C).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20even%20though%20Kamala%20Harris%20can%20speak%20only%20a%20few%20words%20of%20Tamil%20but%20knows%20most%20of%20the%20Tamil%20cuisine.%20%26quot%3BWhenever%20my%20sister%20Mahalakshmi%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Canada%20and%20is%20a%20good%20cook%2C%20visits%20Kamala%2C%20she%20would%20ask%20her%20to%20cook%20and%20put%20the%20food%20in%20the%20freezer.%20Her%20children%20and%20husband%20too%20like%20Indian%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris%20is%20viewed%20as%20a%20role%20model%20in%20her%20mother's%20ancestral%20village%20of%20Thulasendrapuram%2C%20where%20villages%20pray%20at%20the%20main%20temple%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20surprise%20at%20the%20love%20and%20support%20for%20Ms%20Harris%20from%20their%20ancestral%20village%2C%20Dr%20Gopalan%20noted%20that%20India%20holds%20a%20special%20place%20in%20Kamala%20Harris'%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKamala%20is%20an%20American%2C%20but%20India%20is%20very%20special%20to%20her.%20She%20cherishes%20a%20few%20things%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Harris%2C%20Dr%20Gopalan%20says%2C%20treasures%20a%20gift%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20gazette%2C%20he%20had%20taken%20out%20my%20father's%20postings%20in%20the%20government%20of%20India%20as%20a%20joint%20secretary%20and%20when%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20foreign%20service%20in%20Zambia.%20He%20highlighted%20those%20from%20the%20gazette%20and%20gave%20it%20in%20a%20beautiful%20frame%20as%20a%20gift%20to%20Kamala.%20Kamala%20treasures%20it%20because%20it's%20(related%20to)%20her%20grandfather%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BNormally%2C%20she%20can't%20keep%20such%20gifts%20and%20it%20goes%20to%20the%20government.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20they%20let%20her%20have%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20profound%20impact%20of%20the%20grandfather%20on%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20Dr%20Gopalan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20got%20along%20well.%20My%20father%20used%20to%20take%20her%20along%20the%20Besant%20Nagar%20Beach%20during%20his%20walk.%20Kamala%20says%20their%20conversations%20(during%20that%20time)%20impacted%20her%20much%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20recalled%20the%20last%20time%20she%20visited%20Ms%20Harris.%20%26quot%3BI%20visited%20her%20last%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202022%20after%20she%20became%20the%20Vice%20President.%20I%20stayed%20at%20the%20Vice%20President%20house%20for%20four%20or%20five%20days%20and%20that%20was%20a%20very%20pleasant%20thing.%20I%20visited%20her%20office%20and%20she%20was%20kind%20enough%20to%20take%20me%20to%20the%20President's%20office%20and%20showed%20me%20the%20Oval%20Office%20and%20I%20was%20very%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERooting%20for%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20her%20aunt%20wished%20her%20all%20the%20best.%20hoping%20she%20would%20set%20a%20record%20in%20the%20US%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20woman%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724427540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fiv67r3ig_kamala-harris-chitthi_625x300_23_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-presidential-election-when-kamala-harris-gave-her-watch-to-chitthi-aunt-recalls-fond-memories-6403270%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20was%20US%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris'%20time%20to%20shine%20on%20the%20biggest%20night%20of%20her%20political%20life%20on%20Thursday%20as%20she%20accepted%20the%20Democratic%20presidential%20nomination%20before%20an%20ecstatic%20crowd.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-presidential-election-when-kamala-harris-gave-her-watch-to-chitthi-aunt-recalls-fond-memories-6403270%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Devotees%20From%20Pune%20Visit%20Tirumala%20Temple%20Wearing%2025%20Kg%20Gold%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDevotees%20from%20Pune%20visited%20the%20famous%20Tirumala's%20Venkateswara%20Temple%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20wearing%2025%20kg%20gold%20worth%20nearly%20Rs%2018%20crore%20earlier%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20men%2C%20a%20woman%20and%20a%20boy%20visited%20the%20temple%20wearing%20several%20gold%20chains%2C%20gold%20sunglasses%2C%20bangles%2C%20necklaces%2C%20a%20'7'%20number%20gold%20chain%2C%20and%20several%20ornaments%20to%20visit%20the%20temple.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EVIDEO%20%7C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%3A%20Devotees%20from%20Pune%20wearing%2025%20kg%20of%20gold%20visited%20Tirumala's%20Venkateswara%20Temple%20earlier%20today.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn(Full%20video%20available%20on%20PTI%20Videos%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fn147TvqRQz%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fn147TvqRQz%3C%2Fa%3E)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fk38FCr30zE%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fk38FCr30zE%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20(%40PTI_News)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1826849839058956514%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20two%20men%20in%20navy%20blue%20khaki%20suit%20along%20with%20a%20cop%20were%20guarding%20the%20devotees%20as%20they%20sought%20blessings%20at%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ancient%20hill%20temple%20gets%20from%2075%2C000%20to%2090%2C000%20pilgrims%20every%20day.%20Tirumala%20Tirupati%20Devasthanams%20(TTD)%20executive%20officer%20Syamala%20Rao%20earlier%20said%20the%20world-famous%20Sri%20Venkateswara%20temple%20received%20offerings%20worth%20Rs%20125%20crore%20in%20its%20hundi%20(offering%20box)%20for%20the%20month%20of%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao%20said%20over%2022%20lakh%20pilgrims%20visited%20the%20temple%20and%208.6%20lakh%20devotees%20underwent%20ritual%20tonsuring%20at%20the%20hill%20temple%20in%20July.%20The%20temple%20also%20sold%20over%20one%20crore%20laddus%20(consecrated%20sweets).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20temple%20is%20dedicated%20to%20Venkateswara%2C%20a%20form%20of%20Vishnu%2C%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20appeared%20on%20the%20earth%20to%20save%20mankind%20from%20the%20trials%20and%20troubles%20of%20Kali%20Yuga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legend%20says%20that%20Lord%20Sri%20Venkateswara%2C%20also%20k