Ukraine%20has%20entered%20a%20new%20phase%20with%20Kyiv%20crossing%20the%20international%20border%20and%20taking%20control%20of%20several%20Russian%20settlements%20in%20Kursk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20Ukraine%20trip%20can%20work%20toward%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20us%20to%20an%20end%20to%20the%20conflict%20that%20comports%20with%20President%20(Volodymyr)%20Zelensky's%20vision%20for%20a%20just%20peace%2C%20well%2C%20then%20we%20think%20that%20would%20be%20helpful%2C%26quot%3B%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20had%20termed%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit%20to%20Ukraine%20an%20important%20trip.%20Richard%20R%20Verma%2C%20the%20US%20Deputy%20Secretary%20of%20State%20for%20Management%20and%20Resources%20in%20a%20briefing%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20delighted%20about%20this%20visit.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20an%20important%20visit%20--%20Poland%20and%20Ukraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20statement%20issued%20today%2C%20both%20leaders%20expressed%20their%20mutual%20interest%20in%20elevating%20bilateral%20relations%20from%20a%20comprehensive%20partnership%20to%20a%20strategic%20partnership%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-ukraine-visit-pm-modi-holds-talks-with-ukraine-president-in-kyiv-full-joint-statement-6402100%5C%22%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%3A%C2%A0PM%20Modi%20Holds%20Talks%20With%20Ukraine%20President%20In%20Kyiv.%20Full%20Joint%20Statement%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20war%20between%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20began%20on%20February%2024%2C%202022%2C%20was%20bound%20to%20be%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20meeting.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20reiterated%20India's%20stance%20that%20this%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20the%20era%20of%20war%26quot%3B.%20India%20has%20emphasized%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%20to%20find%20solutions%20to%20conflict.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20joint%20statement%20as%20well%20India%20reiterated%20its%20principled%20position%20and%20focus%20on%20peaceful%20resolution%20through%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy.%20The%20Ukrainian%20side%20welcomed%20such%20participation%20by%20India%20and%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20high-level%20Indian%20participation%20in%20the%20next%20Peace%20Summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sides%20agreed%20to%20explore%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20companies%20in%20Ukraine's%20reconstruction%20and%20recovery%2C%20in%20a%20suitable%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20held%20a%20press%20briefing%20in%20Kyiv%2C%20answering%20questions%20on%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit.%20When%20asked%20whether%20India%20suggested%20a%20plan%20to%20end%20the%20conflict%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20having%20our%20own%20thoughts%20and%20discussions%20with%20many%20other%20countries.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20in%20Moscow%20recently%3B%20there%20were%20detailed%20discussions%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%20%26quot%3BPM%20Modi%20shared%20many%20of%20the%20thoughts%20and%20substance%20of%20the%20discussion.%20We%20heard%20from%20President%20Zelensky%20about%20what%20his%20own%20views%20were%20on%20these%20issues.%20So%20it%20was%20a%20very%20back-and-forth%20discussion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20my%20mind%2C%20there%20was%20certainly%20information%20which%20we%20obtained%20here%20and%20I%20am%20sure%20we%20also%20perhaps%20brought%20up%20points%20and%20flagged%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdid-india-suggest-plan-to-end-ukraine-conflict-what-s-jaishankar-said-6402249%5C%22%3ERead%20more%3A%C2%A0Did%20India%20Suggest%20Plan%20To%20End%20Ukraine%20Conflict%3F%20What%20S%20Jaishankar%20Said%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20visited%20Russia%2C%20where%20he%20held%20bilateral%20talks%20with%20President%20Putin.%20A%20month%20later%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20visited%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Russia%20go%20back%20several%20decades%2C%20where%20the%20partnership%20covering%20several%20sectors%20like%20defence%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20bilateral%20trade.%20India%20has%20maintained%20ties%20with%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20came%20into%20existence%20after%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20in%201991.%20Thousands%20of%20Indian%20students%20used%20to%20travel%20to%20Ukraine%20to%20study%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20India%20has%20reiterated%20its%20stance%20that%20it%20consistently%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20cessation%20of%20hostilities%20and%20an%20end%20to%20the%20violence%20but%20Delhi%20has%20maintained%20close%20ties%20with%20Moscow%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20West%20has%20sided%20with%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20last%20met%20Mr%20Zelensky%20in%20June%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G7%20summit%20in%20Italy's%20Apulia.%20In%20the%20meeting%2C%20he%20conveyed%20to%20the%20Ukrainian%20President%20that%20India%20would%20continue%20to%20do%20everything%20within%20its%20means%20to%20support%20a%20peaceful%20solution%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724427480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fkkihncj_pm-modi-and-zelensky_625x300_23_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhite-house-says-pm-modis-visit-to-ukraine-potentially-helpful-6403084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20conflict-hit%20Ukraine%20is%20%26quot%3Bpotentially%20helpful%26quot%3B%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported%20quoting%20the%2