5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentrepreneur%20and%20content%20creator%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20took%20his%20young%20daughter%20to%20a%20swimming%20pool%20in%20Mumbai.%20However%2C%20unlike%20any%20other%20parent%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20set%20a%20time%20limit%20on%20her.%20She%20was%20free%20to%20swim%20and%20frolic%20around%20in%20the%20pool%20for%20as%20long%20as%20she%20wanted%20to%2C%20and%20after%203.5%20hours%20of%20fun%2C%20she%20was%20ready%20to%20go%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20found%20this%20to%20be%20a%20refreshing%20take%20on%20parenting.%20Wouldn%E2%80%99t%20we%20all%20want%20to%20sit%20around%20in%20a%20pool%20for%20three%20hours%3F%20Wouldn%E2%80%99t%20we%20all%20want%20to%20just%20%E2%80%98live%20in%20the%20moment%E2%80%99%20without%20worrying%20about%20time%20or%20running%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%3F%20Why%20then%20do%20we%20impose%20this%20same%20mindset%20and%20put%20our%20children%20in%20the%20rat%20race%20starting%20at%20mere%2018%20months%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%E2%80%99ll%20find%20children%20today%20going%20to%20multiple%20classes%20after%20school%20and%20they%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20time%20to%20sit%20around%20or%20play.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20time%20to%20even%20understand%20where%20their%20interests%20lie.%20And%20the%20biggest%20issue%20is%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20time%20to%20form%20real%20connections%20and%20relationships%20with%20their%20parents%2C%20friends%20or%20other%20family%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20previous%20line%20of%20work%20where%20I%20interacted%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20young%20students%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20many%20of%20them%20were%20opposed%20to%20change.%20They%20were%20often%20too%20set%20in%20their%20ways%20to%20accept%20any%20transformation%20coming%20their%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harpreet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20turning%2035%20or%2040%2C%20usually%20such%20people%20realise%20that%20they%20aren%E2%80%99t%20doing%20what%20they%20love.