y%20Harpreet%20Singh%20Grover%20%7C%20Parenting%20(%40thecuriousparent.harpreet)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20education%20system%20is%20the%20remnant%20of%20the%20Prussian%20model%20of%20schooling%20which%20wanted%20to%20prepare%20factory%20workers%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20curious%20parent%20states%20that%20we%20must%20find%20a%20school%20where%20a%20child%20is%20involved%20in%20an%20interactive%20environment%20filled%20with%20love%20and%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebika%20Chatterji%2C%20Director%20Principal%2C%20JBCN%20International%20School%2C%20Borivali%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20about%20the%20board%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20the%20people.%20Speak%20to%20the%20principal%20and%20teachers%20of%20the%20school.%20They%20should%20speak%20a%20language%20of%20compassion%2C%20care%20and%20follow%20best%20practices.%20The%20school%20should%20focus%20on%20holistic%20development%20of%20the%20child%20and%20must%20take%20charge%20of%20their%20education.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoing%20this%20would%20prevent%20these%20children%20from%20becoming%20adults%20who%20question%20their%20life%20choices%20at%2040%2C%20he%20states.%20What%20this%20boils%20down%20to%2C%20ultimately%2C%20is%20whether%20we%20feel%20happy%20in%20our%20lives.%20If%20the%20child%20sees%20a%20joyful%20adult%20who%20feels%20in%20control%20of%20their%20lives%2C%20they%20will%20learn%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20child%20is%20born%20to%20put%20in%20the%20effort.%20They%20learn%20to%20walk%20and%20talk%20by%20themselves.%20Why%20then%20do%20they%20become%20lazy%20by%20the%20time%20they%20are%2010%20years%20old%3F%20We%20must%20have%20done%20something%20wrong.%20Find%20a%20school%20which%20focuses%20on%20a%20child%2C%20not%20on%20creating%20engineers%20and%20doctors%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20our%20relationship%20with%20our%20partner%20is%20goo