oscow%20remains%20a%20key%20supplier%20of%20oil%20and%20weapons%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20much%20of%20the%20discussion%20between%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Mr%20Zelensky%20was%20about%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Ukraine%20also%20signed%20four%20agreements%20today%2C%20which%20would%20provide%20for%20cooperation%20in%20agriculture%20and%20food%20industry%2C%20medicine%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20humanitarian%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Ukraine%20was%20the%20first-ever%20visit%20by%20an%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20after%20Ukraine%20became%20independent%20in%201991.%20The%20visit%20also%20comes%20amid%20Ukraine's%20fresh%20military%20offensive%20in%20Russia's%20western%20Kursk%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724420160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fp5g0foc_modi-putin-hug_625x300_09_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcultural-gap-says-s-jaishankar-on-western-criticism-of-pm-narendra-modi-and-putin-hug-6401986%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20hugged%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20when%20both%20met%20today%20in%20Kyiv%20to%20discuss%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20issues%20including%20the%20Ukraine-Russia%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcultural-gap-says-s-jaishankar-on-western-criticism-of-pm-narendra-modi-and-putin-hug-6401986%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Snipers%20kill%20knife-wielding%20inmates%20claiming%20to%20be%20IS%20fighters%20who%20seized%20guards%20at%20Russian%20jail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724420100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F08%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-russia-prison-is-islamic-state_6664245.jpg%3F20240823150731%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22ht