eaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F6b3qb9e8_anil-ambani_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20long%20ago%2C%20Anil%20Ambani%20was%20considered%20the%20most%20flamboyant%20industrialist%20in%20the%20country%2C%20exuding%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20energy%20and%20frequently%20in%20the%20news%2C%20from%20Page%20Three%20to%20political%20and%20business%20pages.%20The%20collapse%20of%20his%20business%20empire%20made%20big%20headlines%20and%20became%20a%20matter%20of%20public%20discourse%2C%20from%20chatter%20in%20elite%20circles%20to%20local%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshops%20in%20the%20hinterland.%20A%20bombshell%20has%20now%20arrived%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20report%20from%20the%20markets%20regulator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%2C%20in%20its%20222-page%20report%2C%20has%20severely%20castigated%20Ambani%20and%20his%20associates%20following%20an%20investigation%20into%20multiple%20complaints%20alleging%20the%20siphoning%20of%20funds%20from%20Reliance%20Home%20Finance%20Ltd%20between%202018-19.%20The%20report%20calls%20Anil%20Ambani%2C%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Anil%20Dhirubhai%20Ambani%20Group%20(ADAG)%2C%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20a%20fraudulent%20scheme%20to%20siphon%20off%20funds%20from%20the%20publicly%20listed%20Reliance%20Home%20Finance%20Ltd%20(RHFL)%20by%20disguising%20them%20as%20loans%20to%20nondescript%20and%20financially%20weak%20privately%20held%20companies%20connected%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Cavalier%20Approach'%3A%20What%20The%20Report%20Says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SEBI%20report%20notes%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20also%20a%20peculiar%20case%20where%20the%20company's%20management%20has%20brazenly%20defied%20the%20diktat%20of%20its%20own%20Board%20that%20had%20raised%20concerns%20about%20%60General%20Purpose%20Working%20Capital%20Loans%20(GPCL%2FGPC)%20lending%20and%20asked%20the%20company%20management%20to%20ensure%20compliance%20with%20the%20law.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20further%20adds%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20cavalier%20approach%20by%20the%20company%20management%20and%20the%20promoter%20in%20approving%20loans%20amounting%20to%20hundreds%20of%20crores%20to%20companies%20many%20of%20which%20had%20negligible%20assets%2C%20cash%20flows%2C%20net%20worth%2C%20or%20revenues%2C%20suggests%20a%20sinister%20objective%20behind%20the%20%60loans'.%20This%20sinister%20objective%20becomes%20all%20the%20more%20clear%20when%20the%20relationship%20of%20the%20borrowers%20with%20the%20promoters%20of%20RHFL%20is%20taken%20into%20account.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20SEBI%20has%20barred%20Anil%20Ambani%20and%2024%20other%20entities%2C%20including%20former%20key%20officials%20of%20Reliance%20Home%20Finance%2C%20from%20the%20securities%20market%20for%20five%20years.%20It%20has%20also%20imposed%20a%20penalty%20of%20Rs%2025%20crore%20on%20Ambani%20and%20restrained%20him%20from%20being%20associated%20with%20the%20securities%20market%2C%20including%20as%20a%20director%20or%20Key%20Managerial%20Personnel%20(KMP)%20in%20any%20listed%20company%20or%20any%20intermediary%20registered%20with%20the%20regulator%2C%20for%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SEBI%20report%20is%20likely%20to%20prompt%20other%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20to%20initiate%20investigations%20against%20Ambani%20and%20other%20persons%20whose%20names%20have%20been%20red-flagged%20by%20the%20markets%20regulator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20Startling%20Findings%20From%20SEBI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2062%20loan%20applications%2C%20covering%20an%20amount%20of%20Rs%205%2C552.67%20crore%20were%20approved%20on%20the%20date%20of%20the%20loan%20application%20itself%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E27%20loan%20applications%20amounting%20to%20Rs%201%2C940.58%20crore%20were%20disbursed%20to%20the%20borrower%20on%20the%20date%20of%20the%20application%20itself%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Credit%20Approval%20Memo%20(CAM)%20for%20loans%20amounting%20to%20Rs%205%2C850.19%20crore%2C%20deviations%20from%20due%20process%20were%20recorded.%20The%20nature%20of%20these%20deviations%20includes%3A%20field%20investigation%20waived%2C%20probability%20of%20default%20waived%2C%20eligibility%20criteria%20not%20as%20per%20the%20norms%2C%20no%20creation%20of%20security%2C%20no%20customer%20rating%20undertaken%2C%20escrow%20account%20not%20opened%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20found%20that%20most%20of%20the%20loan%20application%20forms%20were%20left%20blank%2C%20and%20the%20authorised%20signatories%20merely%20signed%20on%20the%20last%20page%20of%20such%20application%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20the%20RHFL%20Board%20explicitly%20instructed%20the%20company%20on%20February%2011%2C%202019%2C%20to%20stop%20disbursing%20any%20further%20GPC%20loans%2C%20RHFL%20continued%20to%20do%20so%2C%20disbursing%20thousands%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees%20with%20impunity%2C%20approved%20by%20Anil%20Ambani%20in%20his%20capacity%20as%20Group%20Head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20at%20the%20time%20of%20disbursal%20of%20the%20GPC%20Loans%2C%20the%20internal%20approval%20memos%20themselves%20recorded%20that%20several%20hundreds%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees%20worth%20of%20loans%20were%20being%20made%20to%20nondescript%20and%20dubious%20entities%20that%20were%20plainly%20and%20utterly%20credit-unworthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20all%20part%20of%20an%20elaborate%20and%20nefarious%20scheme%20undertaken%20to%20divert%20funds%20from%20RHFL%20to%20promoter-linked%20entities%20while%20concealing%20the%20financial%20implications%20of%20their%20actions%20from%20the%20investing%20public.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20company%20eventually%20collapsed%2C%20causing%20immense%20losses%20to%20its%20investors%20and%20the%20broader%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Elaborate%20Scheme%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20facts%20and%20circumstances%20of%20this%20case%20clearly%20indicate%20that%20the%20defaults%20are%20the%20culmination%20of%20an%20elaborate%20and%20coordinated%20design%20to%20move%20funds%20from%20the%20publicly%20listed%20company%20to%20nondescript%20and%20financially%20weak%20privately%20held%20companies%20connected%20with%20the%20Reliance%20ADA%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20a%20preponderance%20of%20probability%2C%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20the%20fraudulent%20scheme%20seems%20to%20be%20Anil%20Ambani.%20It%20is%20also%20apparent%20that%20some%20other%20persons%20in%20key%20management%20positions%20in%20the%20company%20played%20an%20active%20role%20in%20perpetrating%20the%20fraudulent%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20most%20of%20the%20GPCL%20borrowers'%20accounts%20turned%20into%20NPAs%2C%20and%20as%20a%20consequence%2C%20RHFL%20defaulted%20on%20its%20payment%20obligations%20towards%20its%20lenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20public%20shareholders%20have%20been%20left%20high%20and%20dry.%20For%20reference%2C%20as%20of%20March%202018%2C%20the%20RHFL%20share%20price%20had%20closed%20at%20around%20Rs%2059.60.%20By%20March%202020%2C%20as%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20fraud%20became%20clear%2C%20the%20share%20price%20had%20collapsed%20to%20Rs%200.75.%20Even%20to%20this%20date%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%209%20lakh%20shareholders%20invested%20in%20RHFL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724419440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F264rsmig_anil-ambani_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-led-sebi-to-ban-anil-ambani-from-market-and-impose-fine-6402270%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20SEBI%20report%20is%20likely%20to%20prompt