ssing-from-inside-wreckage-13201485%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsuperyacht-sinks-divers-find-body-of-final-person-missing-from-inside-wreckage-13201485%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Can%20The%20BJP%20Survive%20The%20Growing%20Jat%20Discontent%20In%20Haryana%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F3vn1d678_haryana_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20will%20vote%20on%20October%201%20for%20elections%20to%20its%2090%20assembly%20seats.%20The%20Congress%2C%20buoyed%20by%20its%20performance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20growing%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20decade-long%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%2C%20and%20Jat%20discontent%2C%20is%20aiming%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20hopes%20to%20retain%20power%20by%20consolidating%20non-Jat%20votes%20and%20leveraging%20the%20work%20done%20by%20its%20state%20government%2C%20as%20well%20as%20exploiting%20factionalism%20within%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20Inching%20Forward%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20general%20election%2C%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20won%20five%20seats%20each.%20The%20latter%2C%20notably%2C%20had%20won%20zero%20seats%20in%202019.%20While%20the%20BJP%20recorded%20a%2046%25%20vote%20share%2C%20the%20Congress%20received%2044%25.%20Four%20of%20the%20seats%20the%20Congress%20has%20won%20this%20time%20-%20Hisar%2C%20Sirsa%2C%20Sonipat%2C%20and%20Rohtak%20-%20are%20either%20in%20Jat-dominated%20areas%20or%20have%20significant%20Jat%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJats%20make%20up%2027%25%20of%20Haryana's%20population%20and%20are%20the%20most%20influential%20community%20in%20the%20state.%20About%2060%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20has%20come%20from%20this%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20BJP%20appointed%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%2C%20an%20OBC%20leader%2C%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Haryana%2C%20overlooking%20the%20more%20favoured%20Captain%20Abhimanyu%2C%20a%20Jat%20candidate.%20This%20decision%20naturally%20did%20not%20sit%20well%20with%20the%20community%2C%20which%20is%20used%20to%20being%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state.%20Then%2C%20just%20before%20the%20general%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20replaced%20Khattar%20with%20another%20OBC%20leader%2C%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2057%20seats%20in%20Haryana%20where%20the%20Jat%20population%20exceeds%2010%25%20as%20the%20share%20of%20the%20population%2C%20and%2037%20seats%20where%20it%20exceeds%2020%25.%20As%20many%20as%2030%20of%20these%20seats%20are%20in%20the%20Rohtak%20and%20Hisar%20divisions.%20Despite%20winning%20the%20state%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20struggled%20in%20these%20constituencies%2C%20securing%20only%20eight%20and%2012%20seats%20here%2C%20respectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Jats%20Are%20Angry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jats%20are%20dissatisfied%20with%20the%20BJP's%20strategy%20of%20anti-dominant%20caste%20politics%20and%20its%20decision%20to%20deny%20them%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20position.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20party%20replaced%20its%20Jat%20chiefs%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Haryana%20with%20non-Jats%20ahead%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20polls%2C%20didn't%20help%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJat%20leaders%20cite%20the%20Modi%20government's%20alleged%20indifference%20towards%20their%20community%2C%20particularly%20towards%20farmers%20and%20wrestlers%2C%20as%20a%20major%20reason%20for%20their%20frustration.%20The%20farmer%20agitation%20and%20the%20wrestlers'%20have%20only%20amplified%20this%20discontent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Agnipath%20scheme%20too%2C%20which%20reduces%20the%20service%20tenure%20to%20four%20years%20for%20most%20army%20candidates%2C%20has%20angered%20the%20Jats%2C%20who%20send%20a%20large%20number%20of%20youths%20to%20the%20force%20each%20year.%20The%20policy%20change%20amid%20already%20high%20unemployment%20rates%20in%20the%20state%20has%20demoralised%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20JJP's%20Story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202019%20state%20elections%20had%20given%20a%20hung%20verdict.%20Though%20BJP%20still%20emerged%20as%20the%20single-largest%20party%20with%2040%20out%20of%2090%20seats%2C%20it%20had%20to%20form%20a%20post-poll%20alliance%20with%20the%20debutant%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%2C%20a%20splinter%20group%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD).%20The%20JJP%20had%20managed%20to%20secure%2010%20seats%2C%20eight%20of%20them%20being%20in%20Jat-dominated%20areas.%20The%20growing%20Jat%20dissatisfaction%20thus%20led%20the%20JJP%20to%20end%20the%20alliance%20just%20before%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20the%20JJP%20has%20lost%20credibility%20among%20Jats%20and%20failed%20to%20secure%20even%201%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share%20in%20the%20general%20elections.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20party%20has%20split%2C%20with%20a%20faction%20dissatisfied%20with%20Dushyant%20Chautala's%20leadership%20aligning%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Jat%20vs%20Non-Jat%20Election%20On%20The%20Cards%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20election%20is%20increasingly%20becoming%20a%20contest%20between%20Jats%20and%20non-Jats.%20The%20BJP%20is%20aiming%20to%20consolidate%20OBC%2C%20Brahmin%2C%20Bania%2C%20and%20Arora%2FKhatri%20votes%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20seeks%20to%20attract%20Jats%2C%20Muslims%2C%20and%20SCs-three%20groups%20that%20together%20account%20for%20more%20than%2050%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20year's%20general%20election%2C%2064%25%20of%20Jats%20supported%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20(the%20Congress%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20alliance)%20-%20a%20gain%20of%2031%25%20compared%20to%202019%20-%20while%2027%25%20backed%20the%20BJP%2C%20a%20loss%20of%2023%25.%20In%20contrast%2C%20as%20many%20as%2050%25%20Jats%20had%20supported%20the%20BJP%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20SCs%2C%2068%25%20backed%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20-%20a%20gain%20of%2040%25%20-%20while%2024%25%20supported%20the%20BJP%2C%20a%20loss%20of%2034%25%20for%20the%20party%20compared%20to%202019.%20This%20shift%20was%20driven%20by%20opposition%20narratives%20suggesting%20that%20the%20BJP%20might%20alter%20the%20constitution%20and%20end%20reservations%20if%20it%20won%20400%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Polarised%20Election%20Won't%20Help%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20assembly%20election%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20highly%20polarised%2C%20though%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20would%20prefer%20to%20avoid%20this.%20The%20BJP%20has%20made%20Kiron%20Chaudhary%2C%20a%20Jat%2C%20its%20Rajya%20Sabha%20candidate%20from%20Haryana%20to%20signal%20that%20it%20does%20care%20about%20the%20community.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Bhupendra%20Singh%20Hooda%20continues%20to%20emphasise%20the%20'36%20biradri'%2C%20a%20local%20phrase%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20unity%20among%20all%20castes%20and%20communities%20in%20Haryana%2C%20to%20appeal%20to%20other%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20hopes%20that%20the%20JJP's%20split%20from%20the%20INLD%20will%20dilute%20the%20Jat%20vote%2C%20but%20this%20seems%20unlikely%20at%20present.%20The%20party%20also%20hopes%20that%20the%20INLD-BSP%20alliance%20will%20make%20inroads%20into%20the%20Congress's%20SC%20vote%20bank%20and%20split%20the%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Assumptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20leaning%20towards%20the%20Hoodas%20to%20secure%20the%20state%2C%20despite%20some%20calls%20to%20make%20Kumari%20Shelja%2C%20a%20Dalit%2C%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20face.%20The%20BJP%20may%20be%20keen%20to%20exploit%20this%20friction%20within%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20concern%20for%20the%20BJP%20is%20the%20usual%20reduction%20in%20vote%20share%20in%20state%20elections%20following%20general%20elections%20as%20the%20Modi%20%26quot%3Bpremium%26quot%3B%20wanes.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20BJP's%20vote%20share%20dropped%20from%2058%25%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20to%20just%2037%25%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%20held%20six%20months%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20general%20election%20has%20proven%20that%20no%20election%20in%20India%20is%20a%20foregone%20conclusion.%20It's%20true%20that%20the%20Congress%20currently%20holds%20an%20edge.%20But%20whether%20it%20will%20be%20able%20to%20maintain%20this%20advantage%20or%20falter%20due%20to%20overconfidence%20and%20factionalism%20will%20be%20another%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724408220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fgs9m4ht8_jat_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-the-bjp-survive-the-growing-jat-discontent-in-haryana-6400692%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20year's%20general%20election%20has%20proven%20that%20no%20election%20in%20India%20is%20a%20foregone%20conclusion.%20It's%20true%20that%20the%20Congress%20currently%20holds%20an%20edge.%20But%20whether%20it%20will%20be%20able%20to%20maintain%20this%20advantage%20will%20be%20another%20story.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engageme