%2Fus%2Ffked-up-beyond-all-recognition-new-york-rep-pat-ryan-uses-army-slang-for-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F112731599.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffked-up-beyond-all-recognition-new-york-rep-pat-ryan-uses-army-slang-for-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F112731599.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%202%20Whistleblowers%20Used%20WhatsApp%20To%20Stop%20over%203000%20Child%20Marriages%20in%20Beed%20District%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mention%20of%20abuse%20and%20rape.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20a%20social%20worker%20at%20a%20government%20hospital%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Beed%20district%20was%20intrigued%20by%20a%20commotion%20that%20had%20ensued.%20Tatwashil%20Kamble%20(40)%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20hospital%20to%20donate%20blood%2C%20soon%20found%20the%20answer%20%E2%80%94%20the%20death%20of%20a%2017-year-old%20girl.%20While%20the%20cause%20of%20her%20death%20had%20been%20ascertained%20as%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emata%20mrutyu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(death%20of%20a%20woman%20during%20childbirth)%2C%20Kamble%20knew%20there%20must%20be%20more%20to%20it.%20Sadly%2C%20talking%20to%20the%20people%20around%20him%20and%20the%20doctor%20left%20him%20aghast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20revealed%20that%20the%20girl%20had%20been%20to%20the%20hospital%20several%20times%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%20over%20attempted%20pregnancies.%20The%20social%20worker%20was%20quick%20to%20deduce%20that%20this%20girl%20had%20been%20married%20at%20the%20age%20of%2014%20in%20a%20blatant%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330387%2Fias-officer-district-magistrate-saju-vaheed-balika-manch-prevent-child-marriage-south-tripura%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecase%20of%20child%20marriage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20shocking%20to%20him.%20But%20what%20the%20medic%20said%20next%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20just%20one%20of%20many%20such%20cases%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20compelled%20Kamble%20to%20dedicate%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20stopping%20child%20marriages%20in%20Beed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20this%2C%20he%20says%20that%20while%20a%20majority%20of%20such%20cases%20were%20bracketed%20as%20%E2%80%98maternal%20deaths%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20real%20cause%20of%20death%20is%20child%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamble%20was%20joined%20by%20Ashok%20Tangde%20(55)%20in%20his%20quest%20to%20put%20a%20halt%20to%20this%20widespread%20practice.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20(CWC)%20%E2%80%94%20an%20autonomous%20institution%20formed%20under%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%20(2015)%20%E2%80%94%20the%20duo%20has%20been%20working%20to%20ensure%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346951%2Fassam-pallabi-ghosh-impact-and-dialogue-foundation-child-human-trafficking-rehabilitation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafer%20world%20for%20girls%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Beed%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-1724157436.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tatwashil%20Kamble%20and%20Ashok%20Tangde%20have%20been%20working%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20stopping%20child%20marriages%20in%20India%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-1724157436.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-1724157436-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-1724157436-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fch