have%20been%20enrolling%20the%20survivors%20of%20child%20violence%20and%20child%20marriages%20in%20schools%2C%20counselling%20families%2C%20enabling%20access%20to%20government%20schemes%20that%20would%20benefit%20girls%2C%20and%20following%20up%20until%20the%20girl%20reaches%2018%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20put%20rape%20survivors%20in%20touch%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F67868%2Fvillage-protection-committee-sugarcane-labour-balamitras%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echild%20protection%20services%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20these%20cases%2C%20simply%20giving%20them%20financial%20aid%20is%20not%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kamble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20the%20survivors%20are%20young%20children%2C%20while%20some%20are%20even%20disabled.%20They%20need%20to%20have%20their%20documents%20in%20order%20to%20make%20a%20strong%20case.%20We%20help%20them%20with%20this%2C%20connect%20them%20with%20district-provided%20lawyers%2C%20and%20guide%20them%20with%20how%20to%20approach%20court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20the%20nobility%20of%20their%20work%2C%20people%20in%20rural%20Beed%20do%20not%20appreciate%20their%20meddling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutting%20this%20case%20into%20point%2C%20Kamble%20tells%20the%20story%20of%20a%20young%20girl%20Anjali%20(name%20changed)%20who%20contacted%20him%20for%20help%20as%20she%20was%20being%20coerced%20into%20marriage.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20tipped%20off%20the%20media%20and%20police%2C%20and%20headed%20to%20the%20location%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-3_11zon-1724158548.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Talks%20are%20held%20with%20the%20famil