200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-4_11zon-1724158658-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-4_11zon-1724158658-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-4_11zon-1724158658-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-4_11zon-1724158658-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362115%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20youth%20of%20the%20villages%20of%20Beed%20is%20part%20of%20Tatwashil%20and%20Ashok%E2%80%99s%20endeavours%20to%20stop%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20district%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tatwashil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivekanand%20Ashok%20Giri%2C%20a%20village%20head%2C%20seconds%20this.%20%E2%80%9CTatwashil%20and%20Ashok%20take%20immediate%20action%20when%20they%20get%20a%20complaint%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F107569%2F12-classmates-rescued-rajasthan-child-bride-jaipur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echild%20marriage%3C%2Fa%3E%20happening.%20They%20work%20closely%20with%20us%20and%20the%20village%20authorities%20to%20do%20this.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20month%2C%20Beed%20sees%20around%20five%20child%20marriages%20nowadays.%20We%20are%20successful%20in%20stopping%20many%20of%20these.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlowing%20the%20whistle%20on%20a%20practice%20that%20has%20been%20customary%20for%20years%20now%2C%20must%20be%20tough%2C%20I%20assume.%20Kamble%20mirrors%20the%20sentiment.%20But%20he%20insists%20that%20in%20every%20undertaking%20of%20good%20work%2C%20there%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20some%20resistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20an%20anecdote%20of%20his%20college%20days%2C%20when%20he%20was%20pursuing%20his%20MSW%20(Masters%20in%20Social%20Work)%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20very%20little%20awareness%20about%20blood%20donation%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20started%20working%20with%20a%20few%20friends%20to%20organise%20camps%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20donate%20blood.%20But%20the%20donors%E2%80%99%20parents%20weren%E2%80%99t%20too%20happy%20about%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20would%20berate%20him%20for%20forcing%20their%20wards%20into%20giving%20blood%20which%20they%20believed%20would%20%E2%80%9Cmake%20them%20less%20human%E2%80%9D.%20But%20gradually%2C%20the%20notion%20was%20dispelled%20and%20Kamble%20became%20the%20first%20point%20of%20contact%20in%20cases%20where%20someone%20needed%20blood%20for%20a%20relative%20or%20friend.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20his%20work%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F208322%2Fbengaluru-teen-teacher-death-blood-donation-community-inspiring-india-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblood%20donation%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20connected%20him%20with%20doctors%2C%20paramedics%2C%20social%20workers%20and%20others%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20network%20that%20he%20now%20relies%20on%20for%20information%20on%20child%20marriages%20in%20Beed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20as%20Kamble%20interjects%2C%20technology%20has%20proved%20very%20resourceful%2C%20especially%20WhatsApp.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20send%20the%20victims%E2%80%99%20details%20and%20pictures%20to%20the%20authorities%20and%20the%20nearest%20social%20worker.%20It%20speeds%20things%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%20Prior%20to%202015%2C%20when%20the%20app%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20as%20popular%2C%20he%20says%20it%20was%20tough%20navigating%20cases%20and%20a%20slow%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-5_11zon-1724158797.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%20the%20years%20Tatwashil%20and%20Ashok%20have%20stopped%20over%203000%20child%20marriages%20and%20helped%20hundreds%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20survivors%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-5_11zon-1724158797.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-5_11zon-1724158797-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-5_11zon-1724158797-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-5_11zon-1724158797-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-5_11zon-1724158797-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362120%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOver%20the%20years%20Tatwashil%20and%20Ashok%20have%20stopped%20over%203%2C000%20child%20marriages%20and%20helped%20hundreds%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20survivors%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tatwashil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20get%20tip-offs%20on%20a%20call.%20Then%20we%20would%20head%20to%20the%20authorities%20and%20collect%20documents.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20hearsay%20and%20paperwork.%20It%20was%20a%20hassle.%E2%80%9D%20He%20shares%20a%20few%20anecdotes%20of%20how%20vital%20information%20like%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20age%20got%20lost%20in%20conversation%20once%20or%20twice.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20reached%20the%20location%20and%20found%20out%20that%20the%20bride%20was%20well%20above%2018%20years%20old.%20We%20had%20dinner%20there%20and%20headed%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20in%20a%20lighter%20vein.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20in%20cases%20where%20there%20is%20an%20underage%20girl%20being%20wedded%20off%2C%20the%20duo%20maintain%20that%20halting%20a%20wedding%20is%20just%20the%20first%20step.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20then%20counsel%20the%20family%20to%20understand%20what%20led%20to%20them%20taking%20this%20step%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tangde%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20a%20police%20case%20is%20registered%20under%20The%20Prohibition%20of%20Child%20Marriage%20Act%2C%202006%20against%20the%20adults%20involved.%20If%20the%20marriage%20is%20consummated%2C%20the%20man%20is%20charged%20under%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fwhat-is-pocso-understanding-indias-landmark-child-abuse-law%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProtection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%3C%2Fa%3E%20(POCSO)%20while%20the%20CWC%20takes%20the%20underage%20girl%20under%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20one%20of%20the%20most%20recent%20cases%2C%20Kamble%20says%20they%20got%20a%20tip-off%20about%20a%20child%20marriage%20that%20had%20already%20taken%20place%20a%20few%20weeks%20prior.%20%E2%80%9CI%20informed%20the%20%3Cem%3Egram%20sevika%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20asked%20her%20to%20go%20to%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20home.%20For%20three%20days%2C%20no%20one%20answered%20the%20door.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20fourth%20day%2C%20the%20group%20led%20by%20Kamble%20reached%20the%20house%20at%206%20am.%20They%20spoke%20to%20the%20girl%2C%20helped%20her%20re-register%20in%20the%20local%20school%2C%20and%20then%20proceeded%20to%20file%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20family.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20girl%20is%20studying%20now%20and%20is%20happy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kamble%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsk%20the%20duo%20about%20their%20most%20challenging%20case%20and%20they%20respond%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20case%2C%20but%20instead%20a%20period%20of%20time.%20%E2%80%9CChild%20marriages%20peaked%20in%20Beed%20amid%20the%20COVID-19-induced%20lockdown.%20We%20have%20more%20than%201%2C300%20villages%20here%20and%20each%20village%20witnessed%2010%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kamble%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20gatherings%20were%20less%20crowded%20and%20not%20many%20people%20in%20the%20village%20knew%20about%20these%20weddings%20because%20of%20social%20distancing%20made%20it%20tougher%20for%20the%20duo%20to%20track%20down%20the%20miscreants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20each%20case%20they%20solve%2C%20the%20duo%20says%20it%20increases%20their%20will%20to%20do%20better.%20And%20each%20time%20they%20hear%20of%20a%20survivor%20who%20has%20risen%20to%20success%20despite%20the%20odds%2C%20it%20makes%20them%20proud.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20recently%2C%20one%20of%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20fathers%20came%20to%20us%20with%20%3Cem%3Epedhas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(milk%20sweets)%20to%20celebrate%20his%20daughter%20completing%20her%20BHMS%20degree%20(Bachelor%20of%20Homoeopathic%20Medicine%20and%20Surgery).%20The%20girl%20was%20rescued%20by%20us%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20another%20story%20of%20a%20girl%20who%20recently%20scored%2093%20percent%20in%20her%20board%20exams.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20age%20of%2014%2C%20we%20had%20stopped%20her%20from%20being%20married%20off%20and%20had%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355387%2Fmeru-international-school-tellapur-hyderabad-migrant-workers-children-daycare-learning-centre%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenrolled%20into%20school%20%3C%2Fa%3Eonce%20again.%20Her%20achievement%20is%20great.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20stories%20are%20heartening%20for%20Tangde%20and%20Kamble%2C%20they%20say%20the%20end%20goal%20is%20a%20world%20where%20girls%20do%20not%20need%20saving.%20A%20world%20where%20freedom%20will%20reign%20without%20fighting%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%