20of%20aspirants%20continue%20to%20live%20in%20small%2C%20windowless%20PGs%20in%20popular%20and%20crowded%20areas%20of%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%2C%20Old%20Rajendra%20Nagar%20(ORN)%2C%20Patel%20Nagar%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20becoming%20an%20officer%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20believed%20that%20aspirants%20need%20to%20relocate%20to%20the%20capital%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20UPSC%20exam%20and%20that%20they%20cannot%20clear%20the%20exam%20without%20coaching.%20This%20issue%20was%20also%20highlighted%20once%20again%20when%20three%20aspirants%20recently%20lost%20their%20lives%20after%20drowning%20in%20the%20waterlogged%20basement%20of%20a%20coaching%20institute%20following%20continuous%20rainfall%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Akash%20Chavda%2C%20who%20cleared%20the%20UPSC%20examination%20in%202023%20with%20an%20All-India%20Rank%20of%201007%2C%20busts%20this%20misconception.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDelhi%20is%20overcrowded%20with%20aspirants%20and%20this%20also%20puts%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20the%20infrastructure%20there.%20When%20I%20visited%20ORN%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20felt%20disgusted%20and%20suffocated.%20There%2C%20aspirants%20compromise%20on%20everything%20from%20rents%20to%20quality%20food.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20really%20do%20not%20need%20to%20go%20to%20Delhi%20for%20preparation.%20This%20could%20have%20been%20true%20a%20few%20years%20back%20when%20there%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20online%20resources%20and%20guidance.%20If%20you%20feel%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20atmosphere%20for%20studies%20at%20home%2C%20you%20can%20rent%20some%20property%20in%20a%20nearby%20town%20and%20join%20a%20library.%20While%20it%20is%20not%20important%20to%20go%20to%20Delhi%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20have%20a%20mentor%20and%20a%20structured%20study%20routine%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Akash%2C%20who%20himself%20sought%20guidance%20from%20a%20retired%20DFO%20(Divisional%20Forest%20Officer)%20during%20his%20preparation%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat-based%20Akash%20had%20prepared%20for%20one%20of%20the%20challenging%20examinations%20of%20the%20country%20from%20the%20comforts%20of%20his%20home%20in%20a%20small%20village%20of%20Somnath%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20experience%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20options%20of%20preparing%20for%20the%20exam%20by%20joining%20the%20coaching%20centres%20in%20Gandhinagar%20or%20Ahmedabad%20but%20I%20chose%20to%20remain%20in%20my%20village.%20I%20never%20felt%20left%20out.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20felt%20privileged.%20My%20mornings%20started%20with%20chirping%20birds%20and%20fresh%20air.%20Whenever%20I%20felt%20stressed%20out%2C%20I%20would%20spend%20time%20with%20my%20family.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-1-1724393529.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Akash%20(second%20from%20left)%20is%20grateful%20to%20his%20cousin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20daily%20wage%20mason%20by%20profession%20%E2%80%94%20who%20showed%20him%20unwavering%20support.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-1-1724393529.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-1-1724393529-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-1-1724393529-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-1-1724393529-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fakash-chavda-1-1724393529-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362690%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAkash%20(second%20from%20left)%20is%20grateful%20to%20his%20cousin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20daily%20wage%20mason%20by%20profession%20%E2%80%94%20who%20showed%20him%20unwavering%20support.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecuring%201007%20rank%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20in%20the%20Indian%20Railway%20Management%20Service%20(IRMS).%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20Akash%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20his%20preparation%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20hostel%20room%20to%20UPSC%20hall%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkash%E2%80%99s%20journey%20to%20success%20was%20filled%20with%20challenges%2C%20perseverance%2C%20and%20a%20strong%20determination%20to%20achieve%20his%20dreams.%20When%20he%20was%20just%20three%20years%20old%2C%20he%20lost%20his%20mother.%20While%20dealing%20with%20the%20terrible%20blow%2C%20it%20was%20difficult%20for%20his%20father%20to%20look%20after%20him%20as%20he%20worked%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20Akash%20was%20enrolled%20in%20a%20hostel.%20However%2C%20he%20lost%20his%20father%20as%20well%20in%20a%20tragic%20road%20accident%20when%20he%20was%20studying%20Class%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20met%20him%20only%20twice%20in%20seven%20years.%20Suddenly%2C%20I%20felt%20I%20had%20no%20one%20left.%20My%20younger%20sister%20also%20lived%20with%20a%20relative%2C%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20away%20from%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20glimmer%20of%20hope%20in%20this%20bleak%20moment%20in%20his%20life%20came%20when%20his%20cousin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20daily%20wage%20mason%20by%20profession%20%E2%80%94%20showed%20him%20unwavering%20support.%20He%20not%20only%20welcomed%20him%20into%20his%20small%20one-room%20tin%20shed%20house%20but%20also%20treated%20him%20like%20his%20own%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20whatever%20I%20am%20is%20because%20of%20him.%20His%20sacrifices%20kept%20motivating%20me.%20He%20was%20not%20financially%20stable%20and%20he%20had