0duo%20concede%20that%20their%20favourite%20bonding%20moments%20happened%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20when%20they%E2%80%99d%20settle%20down%20for%20the%20night.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20exhausted%2C%20sleepy%20and%20hungry%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20speak%20about%20different%20topics%3B%20topics%20that%20many%20parents%20would%20not%20broach%20with%20their%20kids.%20My%20dad%20would%20listen%20to%20my%20thoughts%20and%20it%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20my%20opinions%20were%20validated%2C%20heard%2C%20and%20recognised%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98No%20situation%20is%20hopeless%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20trip%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Thang%20(the%20northernmost%20village%20in%20India)%2C%20Angelica%20learnt%20two%20important%20lessons%20%E2%80%94%20help%20will%20always%20come%2C%20and%20until%20it%20does%2C%20stay%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20driving%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282723%2Fbest-homestays-in-ladakh-things-to-do-in-leh-local-experience%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPangong%20Lake%3C%2Fa%3E%20(the%20world%E2%80%99s%20highest%20saltwater%20lake)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9COn%20our%20way%2C%20we%20came%20across%20a%20patch%20of%20land%20that%20was%20completely%20deserted%20without%20a%20trace%20of%20civilisation.%20It%20was%20an%20eerie%20sight.%E2%80%9D%20While%20riding%20through%20this%20dystopian%20landscape%2C%20the%20duo%20felt%20snow%20falling%20steadily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20weren%E2%80%99t%20wearing%20warm%20clothes%2C%20had%20lost%20signal%20and%20so%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20access%20maps.%20It%20was%20beginning%20to%20get%20dark%20and%20we%20were%20scared%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20While%20Ajay%20continued%20riding%20undeterred%2C%20his%2017-year-old%20pillion%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20as%20calm.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20roads%20in%20Ladakh%20are%20incredibly%20nar