le%20in%20our%20journey.%20For%20example%2C%20our%20project%20to%20create%20park%20benches%20from%20recycled%20plastic%20required%20us%20to%20develop%20new%20methods%20and%20designs%20for%20processing%20and%20moulding%20the%20plastic%20waste.%20It%20showed%20us%20that%20being%20open%20to%20new%20ideas%20and%20continuously%20improving%20our%20processes%20can%20lead%20to%20successful%20outcomes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20the%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Delhi-based%20startup%2C%20the%20process%20begins%20with%20gathering%20plastic%20waste%20from%20various%20sources%2C%20including%20informal%20waste%20workers%20who%20collect%20materials%20from%20different%20locations.%20They%20also%20collaborate%20with%20NGOs%2C%20housing%20societies%2C%20and%20colleges%20to%20run%20awareness%20campaigns%20and%20collect%20plastic%20through%20source%20segregation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20collecting%20the%20plastic%20waste%2C%20we%20sort%20and%20clean%20it%20thoroughly.%20After%20the%20plastic%20waste%20is%20collected%2C%20it%20is%20meticulously%20sorted%20to%20separate%20different%20types%20of%20plastic.%20This%20sorting%20process%20is%20crucial%20because%20different%20plastics%20have%20different%20properties%20and%20melting%20points%2C%20which%20affect%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20final%20product%20as%20well%20as%20the%20recyclability%20of%20the%20recycled%20products.%20Hence%20we%20do%20not%20mix%20different%20plastic%20types%20ensuring%20it%20is%20again%20recyclable%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sonal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%E2%80%99s%20their%20%E2%80%98value-based%20recycling%20technology%E2%80%99%20that%20makes%20%3Cem%3Eeconscious%20%3C%2Fem%3Eunique%20and%20impactful%2C%20argues%20Sonal.%20Unlike%20traditional%20recycling%20methods%2C%20which%20often%20produce%20low-quality%20items%2C%20she%20claims%20their%20approach%20ensures%20that%20the%20recycled%20plastic%20products%